 Galvatron frowned. He doubted he was going to be able to keep her for long. 
"Magnus is probably runnign around with his maximals...." he trailed off. He 
had nothing to say. She was obviously uncomfortable. He stood up. " I must go 
to the bridge to can join me we can scan for your friends or there is a 
quarters vacant down there." he pointed. "You can rest there if you need to" 
he walked off towards the bridge. he saw Guiledart workin hard in the lab. He 
comm'd shredder. "Shredder whats your situation?"
